commit_message:
WIP Doc fixes: PDF generation, cleanup

- add the pdf-docs tox environment according the established guidelines,
  and add sphinxcontrib-svg2pdfconverter as a new requirement;
- docs tox environment: clean up only the generated html, not the entire
  build directory;
- only show the sample sahara.conf file when the HTML generator is used,
  according the guidelines;
- disable the too smart smartquotes option for the latex builder;
- clean the configuration (some options are provided by
  the required version of openstackdocstheme);
- remove the heavly outdated and probably broken support
  for publishing on readthedocs.

Story: 2006117
Task: 35486
Change-Id: I6f5384c0cb4f6cf6e24d6877eaa9bfd3bafe5f60
